* Stop & Restart\nJob Runs
** Stop Active Run
***_ Runs tab → stop button
***_ Cancel specific run
***_ Cancel runs (multiple)
***_ Cancel all queued runs
** When to Stop
***_ Excessive resource use
***_ Processing incorrect data
***_ Immediate intervention needed
** Restart Continuous Jobs
***_ Exponential backoff state
***_ Shows consecutive failures
***_ Shows next retry time
***_ Restart run button
** Restart Effect
***_ Cancels active run
***_ Resets retry period
***_ Starts new run immediately
@endmindmap
